      mediaSrc: {"mp3":["https://alioss.gcores.com/uploads/audio/baea518c-5506-4c6d-9eba-96a6cb813bcc.mp3"]},
      timelines: [{"id":96744,"media_id":1612,"at":21,"title":"开场 BGM","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/10b7719d-bf3c-47b9-a615-1885bc74ebdd.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/10b7719d-bf3c-47b9-a615-1885bc74ebdd_limit.png"}},"content":"欢迎您收听本期新闻电台节目。您现在听到的开场 BGM 是动画《军火女王》的OP 《Borderland》。","quote_href":"https://music.163.com/#/song?id=26118369","created_at":"2019-04-06T10:51:59.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T10:54:56.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96746,"media_id":1612,"at":97,"title":"迷你MD","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/cf13ba30-bbb5-4c37-b580-cc3b17ef4101.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/cf13ba30-bbb5-4c37-b580-cc3b17ef4101_limit.png"}},"content":"在 SEGA FES 2019 上，公布了迷你 MD 的具体详情。该主机将在9月19日全球范围内发售，标准版售价6980日元，双手柄同捆版售价8980日元，其中内含40款作品，有10款作品已经确定。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107987","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:06:47.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:07:09.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96747,"media_id":1612,"at":108,"title":"宣传片","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/8c81046d-0e81-4c9f-9fc1-a98c7936f398.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/8c81046d-0e81-4c9f-9fc1-a98c7936f398_limit.jpg"}},"content":"在上周末的 SEGA FES 2019 中，世嘉正式公布了 Mini MD，3号在官推上放出了第一部宣传视频，其中介绍了首波收录的大作。在其中我们除了能看到《索尼克2》、《噗哟噗哟》、《光明力量》这些最早公布的大作以外，还能看到《火枪英雄》、《漫画地带》、《吸血鬼杀手》等这些让人眼前一亮的硬货。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108155","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:07:31.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:08:11.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96748,"media_id":1612,"at":136,"title":"再做一遍","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/47053b59-17a0-4927-abb3-1f36ec6db967.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/47053b59-17a0-4927-abb3-1f36ec6db967_limit.png"}},"content":"之前任天堂、SNK、索尼这些厂家都将自己的经典游戏机又做了一遍拿出来卖，收录了不少老游戏。这有可能是未来游戏发展的一个趋势。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:11:15.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:13:52.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96749,"media_id":1612,"at":152,"title":"辞退 Richard Garfield","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/70147088-ab6f-4f0b-9abf-02f637a8c37f.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/70147088-ab6f-4f0b-9abf-02f637a8c37f_limit.jpg"}},"content":"此前提到的 Valve 将旗下多名员工辞退有了进一步消息， Artibuff 联系到了《Artifact》的主创设计师 Richard Garfield ，他确认V社解除了与他的工作合同，他与几位《Artifact》核心开发人员现在已经不在V社工作。图中左侧为 Richard Garfield 。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107177","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:15:14.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:15:52.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96750,"media_id":1612,"at":161,"title":"正在反思","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/0cfacc42-abb0-4f27-a20d-9ba2c5600158.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/0cfacc42-abb0-4f27-a20d-9ba2c5600158_limit.jpg"}},"content":"V社推出的以《DOTA 2》为世界观卡牌游戏《Artifact》在推出之后可以说是未火先凉，而近7天的玩家峰值人数为467人，官方也承认了游戏在游戏设计、经济体、游戏的社交体验及其他方面的各种问题，宣布将暂停日常更新，转而发力重做方面。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107996","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:19:20.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:19:48.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96751,"media_id":1612,"at":208,"title":"《Splatoon 2》四月祭典","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/6f3e2cbb-c424-4ebf-b02f-a09404141dc9.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/6f3e2cbb-c424-4ebf-b02f-a09404141dc9_limit.jpg"}},"content":"在3月30日的2019任天堂北美公开赛上，除了公布了 Ver.4.6.0 更新与12种新贴牌武器之外，还宣布了四月份的祭典主题「龟兔赛跑」。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108013","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:22:06.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:22:37.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96752,"media_id":1612,"at":218,"title":"春季节日","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/e3bb6c4c-b530-4851-8040-0f4e27f19157.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/e3bb6c4c-b530-4851-8040-0f4e27f19157_limit.jpg"}},"content":"四月份的祭典依旧是一场全服祭典，时间跨度为48小时，名称为「春季节日」。不同服务器祭典的开始时间稍有不同，日服时间为 4月19日 16:00 - 4月21日 16:00；美服时间为4月20日 06:00 - 4月22日 06:00。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108013","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:23:08.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:24:07.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96753,"media_id":1612,"at":241,"title":"《新樱花大战》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/5d8b63a2-b320-40ac-81a7-99965be2fb6f.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/5d8b63a2-b320-40ac-81a7-99965be2fb6f_limit.png"}},"content":"正在举办的 SEGA FES 2019 上，《新樱花大战》正式公布。本作的故事舞台设定在《樱花大战V》的12年后的帝都·东京。主人公神山诚十郎将率队“新·帝国华击团”守护和平，本作将于冬季登陆 PS4 平台。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107984","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:26:00.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:28:25.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96754,"media_id":1612,"at":285,"title":"太正时代","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fad8ae53-dede-4af8-a164-7c6e42711033.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fad8ae53-dede-4af8-a164-7c6e42711033_limit.png"}},"content":"此处勘误。游戏发生的时间是以日本历史上的大正时代为原型而虚构的“太正时代”，但这个古今东西大众文化虚实交错的时代看起来有一种昭和的感觉。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:29:37.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-07T14:01:41.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96755,"media_id":1612,"at":335,"title":"像绊爱","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/3f4b6833-d801-4397-a354-a9d95e3a19bf.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/3f4b6833-d801-4397-a354-a9d95e3a19bf_limit.png"}},"content":"谜之相似。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:32:27.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T21:18:39.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96756,"media_id":1612,"at":402,"title":"《鬼泣5》“血宫模式”","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/8cbb177a-29a8-416f-b83b-f5d57d34557a.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/8cbb177a-29a8-416f-b83b-f5d57d34557a_limit.png"}},"content":"卡普空第一开发部通过推特向玩家们确认，动作游戏《鬼泣5》的免费更新内容“血宫模式”在北京时间1日下午3点正式上线。“血宫模式”下玩家可以选定本作中任意一位主角，在专有模式中挑战越来越困难的敌人配置，对于不少《鬼泣》系列的忠实粉丝来说这也是练习各种华丽连段以及挑战速通的绝佳模式。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108048","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:38:38.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:40:12.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96758,"media_id":1612,"at":437,"title":"公告","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/32f7a4d8-4f7b-4389-8eb8-61d24fad2ef9.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/32f7a4d8-4f7b-4389-8eb8-61d24fad2ef9_limit.jpg"}},"content":"今年的愚人节，Sukeban Games放出了一则不那么像愚人节玩笑，或者说看起来不那么像愚人节玩笑的公告。公告中所说的内容与之前团队在推特上所透露的，“所有人都已经离开委内瑞拉、团队的情况很好”并不同。实际上，从这篇公告看来，Sukeban Games的处境目前已经变得非常糟糕。在文章中他们提到，除了负责音乐制作的June，团队四分之三（共四人）的人依然留在委内瑞拉，包括作者Ironic Lark与美工Kiririn51。而由于委内瑞拉目前动荡的局势与封锁，因此而造成的持续无计划停电等因素已经严重影响到了Sukeban Games对于新作《N1RV Ann-A》的开发。这也解释了他们为何没有放出今年的愚人节玩笑。并且由于家人与朋友都居住于委内瑞拉，团队成员目前都还无法离开委内瑞拉或没有离开的打算。而更加令人不安的是，这篇公告的后半段，Sukeban Games的成员们开始担心随着委内瑞拉局势的恶化，自己的创作会受到干预，而他们的生命甚至都会因此受到威胁。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108081","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:40:36.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:42:29.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96759,"media_id":1612,"at":503,"title":"全受影响","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/76c6ac20-59d2-4abc-999e-9e16085dc7b6.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/76c6ac20-59d2-4abc-999e-9e16085dc7b6_limit.jpg"}},"content":"委内瑞拉的情况一直非常动荡，物价飞涨，食物缺乏。在这种情况下不要说开发游戏受到冲击，人民最基本的生活条件都难以保证。还是希望委内瑞拉的状况能够好转，也希望Sukeban Games 的成员们能渡过难关。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:44:11.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:46:58.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96760,"media_id":1612,"at":517,"title":"黑色冲突模式新图","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/bcbb0449-b654-4aca-b733-b5dcb7903f1c.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/bcbb0449-b654-4aca-b733-b5dcb7903f1c_limit.jpg"}},"content":"使命召唤》官方 Youtube 频道公开了《使命召唤 黑色行动4》“黑色冲突”模式新地图“恶魔岛”的预告片，展示了一些地图中的内容。《使命召唤 黑色行动4》的“恶魔岛” DLC 将在4月3日首先登陆 PS4 平台，之后一段时间才会上架 Xbox One 和 PC 的战网平台。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108091","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:47:15.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:47:52.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96761,"media_id":1612,"at":531,"title":"恶魔岛","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/b5998fd1-1f0f-4f2b-81e9-0eb13b3c263e.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/b5998fd1-1f0f-4f2b-81e9-0eb13b3c263e_limit.jpg"}},"content":"游戏中“恶魔岛”英文原名为 Alcatraz，是现实中存在于旧金山海湾的真实海岛监狱（ 阿尔卡特拉斯岛），看过尼古拉斯·凯奇、肖恩·康纳利与艾德·哈里斯主演的《勇闯夺命岛》的朋友们应该对此非常熟悉（那片子还是迈克尔·贝执导的）。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:49:48.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:50:03.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96762,"media_id":1612,"at":566,"title":"《哆啦A梦 大雄的牧场物语》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/185c6cc9-cfdb-413a-9a5a-acb4dfa63a63.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/185c6cc9-cfdb-413a-9a5a-acb4dfa63a63_limit.png"}},"content":"《哆啦A梦 大雄的牧场物语》6月13日正式发售平台为NS，中文版确定发售，目前尚未公布是否同步。本作的故事发生在有巨大大树的世界“西泽镇”（シーゼンタウン），游戏内容除了《牧场物语》系列的经典内容包括种田、养鸡、养马等等，还能使用哆啦A梦的秘密道具。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108093","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:51:17.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:51:50.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96763,"media_id":1612,"at":624,"title":"不儿童化","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fe8a52b7-d9f0-4379-9c47-f67d4b749449.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fe8a52b7-d9f0-4379-9c47-f67d4b749449_limit.jpg"}},"content":"之前上映的几部《哆啦A梦》剧场版都不太适合儿童观看，里面讨论一些主题比较成人化。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:52:56.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:55:01.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96764,"media_id":1612,"at":658,"title":"《Sky光·遇》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/12afa5e3-1ebe-4ff6-80b3-2883dc837f1a.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/12afa5e3-1ebe-4ff6-80b3-2883dc837f1a_limit.png"}},"content":"由陈星汉开发，网易发行的手游《Sky光·遇》近日正式上线了国服Apple Store预约，并获得了首页推荐。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108104","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:58:01.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T11:58:46.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96765,"media_id":1612,"at":673,"title":"《人类一败涂地》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/6df25630-1b7c-423f-9bc4-575d3f55d648.gif","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/6df25630-1b7c-423f-9bc4-575d3f55d648_limit.gif"}},"content":"《人类一败涂地》正式支持了使用创意工坊来创建地图等玩家自定义内容，此前测试版的创意工坊仅能单机游玩，开发者也等不及看到玩家会有什么样的好点子了。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108137","created_at":"2019-04-06T11:59:02.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T12:00:03.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96766,"media_id":1612,"at":701,"title":"《无主之地3》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/73dd29ca-b12c-44c8-9013-2d4c6de72d96.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/73dd29ca-b12c-44c8-9013-2d4c6de72d96_limit.jpg"}},"content":"2K 官方在3日公开了《无主之地3》的新预告，宣布游戏将于 9 月 13 日登陆 PS4、Xbox One 以及 PC 平台（Epic独占至2020年4月），并且这一作自带中文配音。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108176","created_at":"2019-04-06T12:00:41.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T12:02:22.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96767,"media_id":1612,"at":742,"title":"《无主之地年度版》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/035ebbe5-7bb6-454f-94b4-4ab1ae023898.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/035ebbe5-7bb6-454f-94b4-4ab1ae023898_limit.png"}},"content":"《无主之地》初代高清复刻版本《无主之地 年度版》现已可在 PC 、PS4 以及 Xbox One 上进行预购，其中 Steam 发售的 PC 版将在北京时间4月4日凌晨1点解锁，其他平台玩家可以在4月3日晚10点之后进行游戏，国区售价98元。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108139","created_at":"2019-04-06T12:02:52.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T12:03:18.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96768,"media_id":1612,"at":762,"title":"《符文工厂4：豪华版》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/36656c97-ac84-416f-9a62-f746bdb37ecb.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/36656c97-ac84-416f-9a62-f746bdb37ecb_limit.png"}},"content":"世嘉官方确认《符文工厂4：豪华版》的中文版将会同步上市登录NS，目前已知日版将会在7月25日发售，普通版4980日元，限定版8800日元。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108153","created_at":"2019-04-06T12:06:06.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T12:08:38.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96769,"media_id":1612,"at":792,"title":"《勇者斗恶龙 你的故事》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/8a77bfa4-5707-43cb-bf35-0fa04dcfb5dd.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/8a77bfa4-5707-43cb-bf35-0fa04dcfb5dd_limit.jpg"}},"content":"由日本国民级RPG《勇者斗恶龙》系列改编的全3D动画《勇者斗恶龙 你的故事》，于今日正式发表了声优阵容，同时官方发布了最新预告片。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108202","created_at":"2019-04-06T13:37:43.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T13:38:35.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96770,"media_id":1612,"at":826,"title":"配音演员","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c0c7d8ed-e4ba-4777-ad32-13e2a60c0a4e.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c0c7d8ed-e4ba-4777-ad32-13e2a60c0a4e_limit.jpg"}},"content":"本作请到了佐藤健、有村架纯、波瑠、坂口健太郎、山田孝之总计13位著名演员担任声优。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T13:39:13.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T13:39:33.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96771,"media_id":1612,"at":857,"title":"表情多","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/eb4219e4-e51e-4be1-95c5-e8515e139f10.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/eb4219e4-e51e-4be1-95c5-e8515e139f10_limit.jpg"}},"content":"史莱姆的表情倒是挺丰富的。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T13:40:17.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T13:40:48.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96772,"media_id":1612,"at":892,"title":"我家房子还蛮大的","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/45478f87-7100-4b89-be66-5cdecf79f32d.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/45478f87-7100-4b89-be66-5cdecf79f32d_limit.jpg"}},"content":"唐突杰学","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T13:44:12.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T13:49:30.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96773,"media_id":1612,"at":914,"title":"本田翼","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/303e80d9-9a6e-418e-90f1-5747f8a0c6f5.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/303e80d9-9a6e-418e-90f1-5747f8a0c6f5_limit.png"}},"content":"本田翼（Honda Tsubasa），1992年6月27日出生东京都三鹰市，日本影视女演员，时尚模特。\r\n","quote_href":"https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1317932/","created_at":"2019-04-06T13:58:06.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T13:59:27.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96774,"media_id":1612,"at":941,"title":"G.E.M.EX 系列“伊布朋友”","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/63a7e7ef-4313-4fda-8e66-bb6be9647072.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/63a7e7ef-4313-4fda-8e66-bb6be9647072_limit.jpg"}},"content":"Mega House G.E.M.EX 系列“伊布朋友”将于4月4日开启预订，售价11000日元（不含税），预计将于2019年8月下旬发售。伊布朋友共包含伊布现有的9种形态，伊布、水伊布、雷伊布、火伊布、太阳伊布、月亮伊布、叶伊布、冰伊布、仙子伊布齐聚一堂，相互之间仿佛有互动。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108149","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:01:10.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:01:39.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96775,"media_id":1612,"at":1037,"title":"超梦\u0026梦幻","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/ddf58a93-2b7c-4a34-86e4-fd0886d93094.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/ddf58a93-2b7c-4a34-86e4-fd0886d93094_limit.jpg"}},"content":"G.E.M.EX 系列之前推出过超梦\u0026梦幻这款模型。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:06:46.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:07:21.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96776,"media_id":1612,"at":1059,"title":"《勇者斗恶龙X》国服停运","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/27770831-6fb1-4c58-bb4f-feb845cd9459.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/27770831-6fb1-4c58-bb4f-feb845cd9459_limit.png"}},"content":"4月2日，国服《勇者斗恶龙X》发出公告，宣布正式停服。服务器将在今后一个月内逐步关闭充值和下载通道，并将在2019年5月30日正式停止游戏运营。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108123","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:08:01.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:09:15.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96777,"media_id":1612,"at":1112,"title":"Index VR","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/075393e8-d7a1-48af-b809-7788b574cbd7.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/075393e8-d7a1-48af-b809-7788b574cbd7_limit.jpg"}},"content":"此前报道的 Index VR 有了进一步进展，虽然V社官方的页面并没有提供给我们多少信息，但推特用户 Wario64 发现了 Index VR 头显的商店页面信息，其中除了表示预售将从5月1日开始之外，还确认V社一直在研发的控制器将随着 Index VR 一起发售。 \r\n根据已经删除的页面，Index VR 将自带开放式耳机，以便玩家在沉浸 VR 世界的同时还能了解外界的情况，头显可以通过 DisplayPort 1.2 和 USB 3.0 连接电脑，玩家需要一块 GTX 1070 或更高配置的显卡才能有良好的游戏体验，而V社一直在研发的控制器 Knuckles 现在已经更名为 Valve Index Controllers ，将随 Index VR 一起公开销售。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108136","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:11:12.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:11:54.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96778,"media_id":1612,"at":1122,"title":"《纪元 1800》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/78d51c0c-b89e-47c6-952f-4da0fb02ac86.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/78d51c0c-b89e-47c6-952f-4da0fb02ac86_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《纪元 1800》是一款由 Ubisoft Blue Byte 工作室制作，育碧发行的城市建造游戏，玩家可以体验史上瞬息万变的精彩时期之一，并发现新科技、新大陆和新社会。而此前育碧与 Epic 的合作也影响到了这款作品，育碧表示将在发售后转为 Epic 销售，不过游戏仍将继续可在 Steam 预购，发售后才会撤下。与此前《全境封锁 2》相同的是，Uplay 用户将不受影响。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108005","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:12:02.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:14:08.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96779,"media_id":1612,"at":1143,"title":"《愤怒军团：重装》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/d6bc6ff1-c544-4d1f-8ebd-b4729be9f9c2.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/d6bc6ff1-c544-4d1f-8ebd-b4729be9f9c2_limit.jpg"}},"content":"从2日起，《愤怒军团：重装》的主机版本就陆续解锁了。4月2日 PS4、Xbox One 的北美和欧洲地区，以及 NS 的北美地区解锁，其他地区（包括PS4港服）则在4月4日解锁。售价9.9美元。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108099","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:14:33.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:15:22.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96780,"media_id":1612,"at":1174,"title":"Rainbow is Magic","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/15e657f7-ffad-4bb8-bce6-8abaf5c5ad70.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/15e657f7-ffad-4bb8-bce6-8abaf5c5ad70_limit.jpg"}},"content":"育碧于北京时间4月1日22点实装了《彩虹六号》愚人节活动，这一主题是“彩虹是魔法”的限时活动可以说是非常的彩色了，育碧中国还将头像更改为了彩虹小马（字面意义），此活动持续至4月8日.","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108090","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:16:00.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:16:42.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96781,"media_id":1612,"at":1193,"title":"疯兔","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c8b4ae55-47be-44c3-b1e9-a160137bd4de.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c8b4ae55-47be-44c3-b1e9-a160137bd4de_limit.png"}},"content":"《荣耀战魂》将开启为期一天的限时活动，育碧旗下的著名搞怪角色疯兔将会加入到战场中，代替原本相互厮杀的士兵。","quote_href":"http://www.ali213.net/news/html/2019-4/418899.html","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:18:52.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:19:21.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96782,"media_id":1612,"at":1202,"title":"特受欢迎","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c16f19aa-e236-43d6-b98f-bd9dbc78c825.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c16f19aa-e236-43d6-b98f-bd9dbc78c825_limit.jpg"}},"content":"疯兔是《雷曼》系列中出现的反派角色，但这个蠢萌的兔子实在是太受欢迎了。所以除了跟他们单出游戏以外，育碧自家的游戏里也有许多关于疯兔的彩蛋。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:19:59.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:21:14.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96783,"media_id":1612,"at":1219,"title":"与Paradox合作","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/4c6a9936-0c59-4223-ad17-62f480e735f2.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/4c6a9936-0c59-4223-ad17-62f480e735f2_limit.jpg"}},"content":"近日，Paradox 宣布与 Alfonso John Romero 及其夫人 Brenda Romero（参与了《巫术》、《龙与地下城》等著名作品的资深游戏开发者）领导的 Romero Games 合作，开发一款基于全新 IP 的战略游戏。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108140","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:21:38.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:22:23.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96784,"media_id":1612,"at":1277,"title":"FC游戏阵容","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/47345269-736a-4946-b215-8a438b069f2a.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/47345269-736a-4946-b215-8a438b069f2a_limit.jpg"}},"content":"3日上午，任天堂在官网公开了四月份的会员服务附赠 FC 游戏阵容，这三款游戏是《超级马力欧兄弟2》、《星际战士》以及《拳无虚发》。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108196","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:23:24.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:24:14.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96785,"media_id":1612,"at":1304,"title":"《星际战士》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fb2d4503-0f81-45da-971e-78a51f5b44b1.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fb2d4503-0f81-45da-971e-78a51f5b44b1_limit.png"}},"content":"《星际战士》是 HUDSON 旗下最知名的空战射击游戏,，玩家为了破坏意欲毁灭人类的人工智能“星间头脑”，操纵战斗机“西瑟”来向由它操纵的敌人发起攻击。游戏一共有16个关卡，在游戏的时候可以通过5个方向的射击来进行机体的强化。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:25:01.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:38:29.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96786,"media_id":1612,"at":1326,"title":"PlayStation商店退款新政","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/69e4864b-1bea-4780-8bf7-8dff4f8c9cd5.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/69e4864b-1bea-4780-8bf7-8dff4f8c9cd5_limit.png"}},"content":"索尼在2日更新了PlayStation商店退款的条款和条件，只要是14天内购买并尚未下载的游戏、DLC、季票和内购物品，都有资格联系客服进行退款，已开始下载的数字内容，除非内容有问题，否则不能退款。预购物品可以在发售前取消，发售后14天内未下载也可以申请退款。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108082","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:38:58.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:40:14.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96788,"media_id":1612,"at":1397,"title":"《小丑》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/49576e93-adfb-4f31-bdc6-4b8ac16c78d0.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/49576e93-adfb-4f31-bdc6-4b8ac16c78d0_limit.jpg"}},"content":"3日晚，华纳兄弟影业放出了华金·菲尼克斯版《小丑》的首部先导预告。本片将于今年 10月 4日登陆北美院线。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108174","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:54:12.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:54:58.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96789,"media_id":1612,"at":1410,"title":"起源故事","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/be5a8802-1f74-4a96-9ac0-43f4b6565aea.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/be5a8802-1f74-4a96-9ac0-43f4b6565aea_limit.png"}},"content":"此次的华金·菲尼克斯版《小丑》将讲述这个 DC 漫画著名反派角色的起源故事。这次的小丑原名为亚瑟·弗莱克（Arthur Fleck），是一个失败的脱口秀演员，被社会大众所忽视，最终成为了哥谭市犯罪与疯狂的标志。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:55:13.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:55:29.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96790,"media_id":1612,"at":1483,"title":"《大侦探皮卡丘》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/14b1120c-9ddf-42d1-80f0-c8a141f2985f.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/14b1120c-9ddf-42d1-80f0-c8a141f2985f_limit.jpg"}},"content":"官方正式宣布《大侦探皮卡丘》将于 5月 10日同步北美登陆内地院线。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108131","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:58:09.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:58:30.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96791,"media_id":1612,"at":1493,"title":"《复仇者联盟4：终局之战》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/3e07d12d-1bf0-4ccb-abfa-9d289d8cf1a9.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/3e07d12d-1bf0-4ccb-abfa-9d289d8cf1a9_limit.png"}},"content":"2日晚，漫威影业再次放出《复仇者联盟4：终局之战》的全新预告，老三大将正面对阵灭霸。本片将于 4月 24日登陆内地院线。\r\n\r\n","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108124","created_at":"2019-04-06T14:58:58.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T14:59:26.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96792,"media_id":1612,"at":1530,"title":"都在预告里","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/1d0d2a40-4117-469c-b5fc-5722734992a7.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/1d0d2a40-4117-469c-b5fc-5722734992a7_limit.png"}},"content":"好多电影的主要内容都剪到了预告里，观众再看一次就没什么新鲜感了。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:00:12.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:01:01.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96793,"media_id":1612,"at":1556,"title":"“鬼玩人”","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/079b2ad7-8cb2-4419-92f6-3ab2951c3c7b.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/079b2ad7-8cb2-4419-92f6-3ab2951c3c7b_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《黎明杀机》的“鬼玩人”角色 DLC 现已正式上线。在《鬼玩人》中扮演 Ash 的布鲁斯·坎贝尔还亲自做宣传，叮嘱玩家“Be Ash,and survive!”","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108158","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:02:23.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:02:46.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96794,"media_id":1612,"at":1594,"title":"《Raid》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/60d98062-63a0-411f-8c51-098d71165a53.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/60d98062-63a0-411f-8c51-098d71165a53_limit.png"}},"content":"以高拟真度，复杂的枪械操作和生存系统以及残酷的多人对战而被玩家戏称为“头铁塔克夫”的射击游戏《逃离塔克夫》最近放出了系列真人短片《Raid》的第一集，这部短片以《逃离塔克夫》的世界观为基础（两队不同阵营的士兵和拾荒者在废城塔克夫中的冲突），整个片子在枪战场面的质量十分惊人。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107995","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:03:30.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:05:33.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96795,"media_id":1612,"at":1637,"title":"硬核","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/cd1cc6fb-a6bb-419d-bd33-e25370f3bdbd.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/cd1cc6fb-a6bb-419d-bd33-e25370f3bdbd_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《逃离塔科夫》是一个非常硬核的射击游戏，游戏里的拟真度非常高，死亡之后的代价也很大。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:06:21.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:08:35.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96796,"media_id":1612,"at":1707,"title":"细节多","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/7133da2b-4f45-46a4-b63d-0b5bc3f32b94.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/7133da2b-4f45-46a4-b63d-0b5bc3f32b94_limit.jpg"}},"content":"单是一个换弹的动作，制作组就下了大功夫去做。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:10:32.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:11:05.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96797,"media_id":1612,"at":1742,"title":"好枪不敢用","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/6b01655d-e127-4ef0-bc81-f667b3c03011.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/6b01655d-e127-4ef0-bc81-f667b3c03011_limit.jpg"}},"content":"因为游戏里的死亡代价很大，玩家死了之后枪就不能拿回来，所以一开始好多玩家都不敢把好枪拿出来用。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:11:47.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:12:29.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96798,"media_id":1612,"at":1780,"title":"HotToy系列玩具","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/1e0340b9-f902-483b-84d2-38a09050c2a1.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/1e0340b9-f902-483b-84d2-38a09050c2a1_limit.jpg"}},"content":"HotToys cosbaby 的《复仇者联盟4：终局之战》系列玩具现在已经可以在我们的淘宝店「机核铺」上购买了。这次一共有 14 款新品，作为系列电影的完结一作，相信这套产品在粉丝心中更是意义非凡。预定将在 4 月 8 日截单，预计在 2019 年第二季度出货。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108073","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:16:37.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:17:55.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96799,"media_id":1612,"at":1791,"title":" BEASTBOX 猛兽匣系列","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/3b69e022-2c5a-4c0c-8de8-58d5467e3128.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/3b69e022-2c5a-4c0c-8de8-58d5467e3128_limit.jpg"}},"content":"52TOYS 原创出品的可变形玩具 BEASTBOX 猛兽匣系列产品及 MEGABOX 系列异形现已上架「机核铺」，推荐喜欢没事鼓捣鼓捣小玩意儿的朋友尝试下！","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/104828","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:18:09.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:23:28.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96800,"media_id":1612,"at":1799,"title":"EVA 福袋","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/13800b34-4486-49f9-ad24-f581374358a7.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/13800b34-4486-49f9-ad24-f581374358a7_limit.png"}},"content":"EVA 新世纪福音战士 露营野餐 福袋已经上架机核铺，包含一款帐篷以及随机一件商品。有兴趣的朋友可以点击链接查看。","quote_href":"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c-s.w4004-21418209351.37.3f1211abnhK8zl\u0026id=589781923839","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:23:38.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:25:33.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96801,"media_id":1612,"at":1817,"title":"灭霸和钢铁侠MK85","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c129a417-0d60-4547-a145-7e6d8464d0e0.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c129a417-0d60-4547-a145-7e6d8464d0e0_limit.jpg"}},"content":" 1/6 的灭霸 3.0和钢铁侠 MK85，以及新的一批《复联4》cosbaby 玩具已经上架机核铺，有兴趣的朋友可以点击链接了解。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108203","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:26:48.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:27:47.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96802,"media_id":1612,"at":1824,"title":"机动奥特曼","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/f191271d-070d-4d32-9b1b-6d545de55083.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/f191271d-070d-4d32-9b1b-6d545de55083_limit.jpg"}},"content":"由 threezero 出品的动画版 1/6 机动奥特曼可动人偶开始接受预订，官方定价：880 元。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107319","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:29:56.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:30:22.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96803,"media_id":1612,"at":1849,"title":"《火炬之光2》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/73663b1b-bf80-4b2a-8a84-eda8d3ac2c3a.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/73663b1b-bf80-4b2a-8a84-eda8d3ac2c3a_limit.png"}},"content":"完美世界与Panic Button达成合作，将为Switch用户带来两款出色的游戏作品，它们是来自Runic Games的《Hob》以及《火炬之光2》，这两款移植版游戏都已确定在2019年内发售。","quote_href":"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1629297238222854351\u0026wfr=spider\u0026for=pc","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:31:13.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:34:59.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96804,"media_id":1612,"at":1853,"title":"《天国：拯救》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c56ce4af-6f86-4505-979c-b64991092968.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/c56ce4af-6f86-4505-979c-b64991092968_limit.png"}},"content":"《天国：拯救(Kingdom Come：Deliverance)》官方宣布调整Steam国区的售价，游戏进行了永久降价。原价248元，现价116元，不到原来的一半了。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:36:15.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:36:46.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96805,"media_id":1612,"at":1861,"title":"《侍魂 NeoGeo合集》 ","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/286dca06-5162-4945-ad5a-4d77c618d30d.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/286dca06-5162-4945-ad5a-4d77c618d30d_limit.jpg"}},"content":"SNK公布了旗下《侍魂》系列的移植作品《侍魂 NeoGeo合集》。　本次的《侍魂 NeoGeo合集》包含了以下六款经典作品：《侍魂》《真侍魂》《侍魂3 斩红郎无双剑》《侍魂4 天草降临》《侍魂零》和《侍魂零 特别版》。本次移植工作由Digital Eclipse工作室负责，该工作室曾经参与制作了《街霸30周年合集》和《SNK 40周年合集》。《侍魂 NeoGeo合集》将支持在线游玩，并且收录街机模式和博物馆模式，本作预计将在今年秋天登陆PS4、Xbox One、Switch和Steam平台。","quote_href":"https://www.vgtime.com/topic/1051374.jhtml","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:41:09.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:44:26.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96806,"media_id":1612,"at":1900,"title":"《马力欧\u0026索尼克 AT 东京奥运会》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/004bebbb-f6bb-4914-b326-6a3d4988080b.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/004bebbb-f6bb-4914-b326-6a3d4988080b_limit.png"}},"content":"马里奥与索尼克携手上阵的人气系列游戏最新作《马里奥\u0026索尼克 AT 东京奥运会》，预计将于2019年冬季上市。本作将登陆NS和街机，在NS平台支持用Joy-Con以体感操作方式来享受奥运竞技乐趣。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/107990","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:41:53.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:50:04.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96808,"media_id":1612,"at":2034,"title":"令和","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/4a842544-5ebe-4843-93d4-97fa02125446.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/4a842544-5ebe-4843-93d4-97fa02125446_limit.jpg"}},"content":"2019年4月1日，日本内阁官房长官菅义伟在记者发布会上公布了新的年号「令和」，将于下月新天皇德仁继位时正式启用。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/108039","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:46:40.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:48:15.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96809,"media_id":1612,"at":2063,"title":"《蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆合集》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fa71f177-9fff-4d78-a71f-b2565f365593.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fa71f177-9fff-4d78-a71f-b2565f365593_limit.png"}},"content":"《蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆》合集已于去年11月27日在Xbox平台发售，合集包括《蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆疯人院》《蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆骑士》与《蝙蝠侠：阿卡姆之城》。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:48:20.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:49:46.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96810,"media_id":1612,"at":2102,"title":"潮汐之潭","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/bbd191ae-b65c-493a-9403-84dbe684dfc3.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/bbd191ae-b65c-493a-9403-84dbe684dfc3_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《全境封锁2》“入侵”大型更新公布了新的预告视频，据点任务“潮汐之潭”将于今日18:30分正式上线，系列首个8人副本“黑暗时刻”行动将于4月25日更新。据点任务“潮汐之潭”将于今日18:30分正式上线，届时会解锁2款全新武器：轻机枪“疫病”和狙击枪“复仇女神”，和适合玩家游戏风格的三款全新套装，还有全新的服装活动以及新PvP地图“麦克奈尔堡垒”。\r\n系列首个8人副本“黑暗时刻”将带领玩家收获新的体验，这次更新中还会加入一些机密任务。在即将推出的第四专长中，其持有特色武器极为致命（从视频中看是一款轻型的加特林机枪），此外拥有首年季票的玩家们可以立即解锁三大专长。","quote_href":"https://www.3dmgame.com/news/201904/3759127.html","created_at":"2019-04-06T15:57:42.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T15:59:17.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96811,"media_id":1612,"at":2126,"title":"没得干了","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fa707e75-8d6f-406f-a22a-882b425aea18.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/fa707e75-8d6f-406f-a22a-882b425aea18_limit.png"}},"content":"天叔实在是没得干了，就重新刷这款烂熟于心的游戏了。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:00:39.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:07:19.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96812,"media_id":1612,"at":2161,"title":"钩索","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/7264bed1-e455-4cdc-9ee9-49b8a81ca397.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/7264bed1-e455-4cdc-9ee9-49b8a81ca397_limit.jpg"}},"content":"钩索在游戏中的用途越来越多，蝙蝠侠可以把敌人拉过来，形成一套连击。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:08:42.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:09:23.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96813,"media_id":1612,"at":2200,"title":"选皮肤","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/85ae4504-0f64-4128-885b-9794ba9c9e54.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/85ae4504-0f64-4128-885b-9794ba9c9e54_limit.jpg"}},"content":"游戏合集自带DLC，玩家打完序章后就可以自定义服装了。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:10:14.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:10:50.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96815,"media_id":1612,"at":2260,"title":"被遗忘的众神","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/1a2da19b-a2f3-429f-9a76-fb0349c36b30.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/1a2da19b-a2f3-429f-9a76-fb0349c36b30_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《恐怖黎明（Grim Dawn）》是一款古典风格的斜俯视角动作RPG游戏，游戏的风格和《暗黑破坏神》以及《泰坦之旅》这类游戏类似。而实际上，其开发商Crate Entertainment就是由当年《泰坦之旅》的开发者组建。游戏在去年10月发售了备受好评（Steam好评率90%）的首部大型DLC“法尔茅斯的灰烬（Ashes of Malmouth Expansion）”之后，又将迎来游戏的第二部重磅DLC“被遗忘的众神（Forgotten Gods）”。玩家将在其中来到Erulan帝国之外“穿过灼热的沙漠、茂盛的绿洲、火山废墟来到一座被太阳毁灭的城市废墟，而这里的秘密本不该被揭开……”","quote_href":"http://www.ali213.net/news/html/2018-3/349579.html","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:14:01.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:14:01.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96816,"media_id":1612,"at":2306,"title":"暗黑2","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/543e74b2-23b3-461d-a386-33f53c58423a.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/543e74b2-23b3-461d-a386-33f53c58423a_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《暗黑破坏神2》是美国暴雪娱乐研发的一款动作类角色扮演游戏，于2000年上市。\r\n游戏中玩家创建属于自己的角色，在一片片暗黑大地上奔跑、杀敌、寻宝、成长，最终打败统治各个大陆的黑暗势力，拯救游戏中的各个种族。游戏提供连线功能，除了惯有的Ipx，MODEM，以及 Direct Link外，Blizzard 设立了一个Server，可供玩家通过Internet，和世界的其它地方的战友一同作战。","quote_href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9A%97%E9%BB%91%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F%E7%A5%9E%E2%85%A1/5078642?fromtitle=%E6%9A%97%E9%BB%91%E7%A0%B4%E5%9D%8F%E7%A5%9E2\u0026fromid=3773338\u0026fr=aladdin","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:14:59.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:18:10.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96817,"media_id":1612,"at":2380,"title":"《机战T》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/5827b3db-2adf-4bbb-a4a4-f69ea3b1f038.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/5827b3db-2adf-4bbb-a4a4-f69ea3b1f038_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《超级机器人大战T》为万代南梦宫出品的《超级机器人大战》系列游戏，首个登陆NS平台的机战作品，将于2019年3月20日发售   。","quote_href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B6%85%E7%BA%A7%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98T","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:20:13.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:21:53.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96818,"media_id":1612,"at":2402,"title":"《傲骨贤妻》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/219a11cc-a640-4840-99df-fdce8d2ada54.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/219a11cc-a640-4840-99df-fdce8d2ada54_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《傲骨贤妻》是日本TBS电视台出品的律政剧，由冢原亚由子、山本刚义、松木彩执导，筱﨑绘里子担任编剧，常盘贵子主演，于2019年1月13日开播。该剧改编自同名美剧，讲述了主人公杏子在丈夫被捕后，为了保护孩子，放弃做全职主妇，重操故业做律师的故事  。","quote_href":"https://movie.douban.com/subject/30372306/","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:22:51.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:24:40.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96819,"media_id":1612,"at":2428,"title":"斗","asset":{"ur