色更丰满。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:34:00.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:35:20.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96824,"media_id":1612,"at":2598,"title":"缜密作战","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/915f3834-397d-41df-a4a2-1d678e41fc68.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/915f3834-397d-41df-a4a2-1d678e41fc68_limit.jpg"}},"content":"小规模的反恐作战更考验这些士兵的军事素养，需要他们做出缜密的判断。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:36:05.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:37:07.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96825,"media_id":1612,"at":2635,"title":"《无主之地2》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/583f3a7b-4ca7-4f27-b54a-cf95fb854764.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/583f3a7b-4ca7-4f27-b54a-cf95fb854764_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《无主之地2》是Gearbox Software开发，2K Games发行的一款第一人称射击游戏，于2012年9月18日发行，是《无主之地》的续作。\r\n该游戏设定在一个名为潘朵拉的星球上，为了寻找“传说宝库”的六名“寻宝猎人”来到了这颗星球上。","quote_href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%8B%E5%9C%B02","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:37:33.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:39:38.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96826,"media_id":1612,"at":2665,"title":"高达节目","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/78d26a78-94ed-401f-9c06-40ca40365b15.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/78d26a78-94ed-401f-9c06-40ca40365b15_limit.jpg"}},"content":"上次大巴、龙马和老白坐下来聊了聊《机动武斗传G高达》，这也是《机战T》的参展作品之一。有兴趣的朋友可以点击链接收听。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/radios/107817","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:42:41.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:44:44.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96827,"media_id":1612,"at":2680,"title":"社畜","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/2d1ec92c-7ba6-46da-b27c-a547cf106fe5.png","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/2d1ec92c-7ba6-46da-b27c-a547cf106fe5_limit.png"}},"content":"本作的男主角叫透才藏，是VTX 联合公司的特殊行动第三组的普通职员。其实这个人和社畜差不多。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:45:51.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:49:35.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96828,"media_id":1612,"at":2756,"title":"“剑鱼II”","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/7ce75b02-ae62-44eb-a0b9-8d0c9315ab79.jpeg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/7ce75b02-ae62-44eb-a0b9-8d0c9315ab79_limit.jpeg"}},"content":"斯派克的座驾是剑鱼号。“剑鱼II”因外形酷似剑鱼而得名，“腹部”搭载的光束炮参考的就是剑鱼式鱼雷轰炸机（Fairy Swordfish）。再从山根喜欢的欧内斯特·米勒·海明威（Ernest Miller Hemingway）的代表作《老人与海》中的剑鱼获得灵感，而且山根认为海明威小说气氛也与斯派克孤高的性格很相符。","quote_href":"http://www.sohu.com/a/245683660_523011","created_at":"2019-04-06T16:57:19.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T16:59:04.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96829,"media_id":1612,"at":2791,"title":"《全金属狂潮》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/dbb79260-13bc-4bb4-b19e-b036178c5b28.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/dbb79260-13bc-4bb4-b19e-b036178c5b28_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《全金属狂潮》（フルメタル・パニック!​）、《全金属狂潮 校园篇》（フルメタル・パニック！ ふもっふ）、《全金属狂潮 The Second Raid》（フルメタル・パニック！ TheSecond Raid）《全金属狂潮（原作小说版）》、（フルメタル・パニック！ （原作小説版））中的机甲都在游戏中出现。","quote_href":"https://www.gcores.com/articles/21267","created_at":"2019-04-06T17:00:24.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T17:01:26.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96830,"media_id":1612,"at":2811,"title":"《蓝宝石之谜》","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/58e04fd0-be21-4e03-ab23-0f4de71d49db.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/58e04fd0-be21-4e03-ab23-0f4de71d49db_limit.jpg"}},"content":"《蓝宝石之谜》由Gainax出品，根据凡尔纳著作《海底两万里》和《神秘岛》改编的39集电视动画，直译《不可思议的海之娜蒂亚》。该作品讲述西历1889年，在巴黎万国博览会会场喜欢发明的少年Jean和马戏团的少女Nadia偶然相遇。遭到意图抢夺Nadia胸前所佩的谜之蓝宝石的格兰蒂斯一伙人的袭击。在格兰蒂斯一伙人的追击中Jean与Nadia出乎意外的冒险旅程开始了。","quote_href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%93%9D%E5%AE%9D%E7%9F%B3%E4%B9%8B%E8%B0%9C/7779177?fr=aladdin","created_at":"2019-04-06T17:02:22.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T17:02:55.000+08:00","comments_count":0},{"id":96831,"media_id":1612,"at":2832,"title":"分享一下","asset":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/131c6585-c3ae-49ed-ad1a-41b8b9ba1b36.jpg","limit":{"url":"/uploads/timeline/131c6585-c3ae-49ed-ad1a-41b8b9ba1b36_limit.jpg"}},"content":"大家可以在评论区里和我们聊聊假期都玩了什么游戏，看了什么电影。","quote_href":"","created_at":"2019-04-06T17:03:36.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-04-06T17:05:12.000+08:00","commen